      "file_path": "policy-management/src/main/java/org/onap/policy/drools/system/PolicyEngineConstants.java",
      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 46,
      "message": "that being the case, do we really want to remove the \"final\" modifier (i.e., do we really want to make this changeable by other code)?",
