      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 46,
      "message": "On the surface, it seemed that changing a static field was cleaner and simpler than changing an internal field of an object -- apparently, that wasn't really the case. So, I put the 'final' back in, and used the suggested approach in 'SimpleLockManagerTest'.",
